Package: task-timer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Task Timer <support@example.com>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34)
Description: Task Timer application
 A cross-platform task timer with GUI and synchronization support.
 Ships the task-timer GUI and the task-timer-daemon headless sync daemon.
